\c 10
\s USamuweli ugcoba uSawuli
\p
\v 1 USamuweli wasethatha umfuma wamafutha, wawathela ekhanda lakhe\x + 9.16. 16.13. 2 Sam. 2.4. 5.3. 1 Kho. 1.39.19.16. 2 Kho. 9.1,3,6. 11.12.\x*, wamanga\x + Gen. 41.40.\x*, wathi: Angithi kungoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikugcobele ukuthi ube ngumbusi phezu kwelifa layo\x + Dute. 32.9. Hlab. 78.71.\x*?
\v 2 Ekusukeni kwakho kimi lamuhla uzafica abantu ababili engcwabeni likaRasheli emngceleni wakoBhenjamini eZeliza\x + Gen. 35.19,20.\x*; njalo bazakuthi kuwe: Obabhemikazi obuyebadinga sebetholiwe, khangela-ke, uyihlo useyekele udaba labobabhemikazi, usenqinekela lina\x + 9.5.\x* esithi: Ngizayenzelani indodana yami?
\v 3 Nxa usudlule lapho waya phambili, uzafika esihlahleni \w se-okhi\w** seThabhori\x + Gen. 13.18.\x*; lalapho uzahlangana labantu abathathu besenyuka besiya kuNkulunkulu eBhetheli\x + Hlu. 20.31.\x*, omunye ephethe amazinyane amathathu, lomunye ephethe amaqebelengwana ezinkwa amathathu, lomunye ephethe imbodlela yewayini.
\v 4 Bazakubuza ngempilo, bakunike izinkwa ezimbili, ozazithatha esandleni sabo.
\v 5 Emva kwalokho uzafika eqaqeni lukaNkulunkulu\x + 10.10.\x* lapho okuhlala khona ibutho lenqaba yamaFilisti\x + 13.3,4. 2 Sam. 8.6,14. 1 Lan. 11.16. 18.13. 2 Lan. 17.2.\x*; kuzakuthi-ke, nxa ufika lapho emzini uzahlangana lexuku labaprofethi besehla endaweni ephakemeyo, laphambi kwabo kulogubhu lwezintambo\x + 9.12.\x*, lesigubhu, lomhlanga\x + Gen. 31.27. 2 Kho. 3.15. Eks. 15.20.\x*, lechacho, beprofetha\x + Gen. 31.27. 2 Kho. 3.15. Eks. 15.20.\x*.
\v 6 LoMoya kaNkulunkulu uzafika ngamandla phezu kwakho\x + 10.10. 11.6. 16.13. Hlu. 14.6,19. Hlu. 3.10. Nani 11.25.\x*, uprofethe kanye labo, uphendulwe ube ngomunye umuntu\x + 10.10. 19.23,24.\x*.
\v 7 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho lezizibonakaliso zikufikela, wena wenze lokho isandla sakho esizakuthola\x + Eks. 4.8. Hlu. 6.17. Luka 2.12.\x*, ngoba uNkulunkulu ulawe\x + Josh. 1.5.\x*.
\v 8 Uzakwehla phambi kwami uye eGiligali\x + 11.14,15. 13.4. Josh. 5.9.\x*; khangela-ke, ngizakwehlela kuwe ukuze nginikele iminikelo yokutshiswa, ngihlabe imihlatshelo yeminikelo yokuthula. Uzalinda insuku eziyisikhombisa ngize ngifike kuwe, ngikutshele lokho ozakwenza\x + 13.8.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Kwasekusithi lapho esefulathele ukuthi asuke kuSamuweli, uNkulunkulu wamnika enye inhliziyo; lazo zonke lezizibonakaliso zeza mhlalokho.
\v 10 Lapho sebefikile khona eqaqeni\x + 10.5.\x*, khangela, ixuku labaprofethi lamhlangabeza\x + 19.20.\x*; uMoya kaNkulunkulu wasefika ngamandla phezu kwakhe, waprofetha phakathi kwabo\x + 10.6.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekusithi bonke ababemazi mandulo bebona ukuthi, khangela, uprofetha labaprofethi, abantu bathi, omunye komunye: Kuyini lokhu okwehlele indodana kaKishi? Kanti uSawuli laye uphakathi kwabaprofethi\x + 19.24. Mat. 13.54,55.\x*?
\v 12 Kwasekuphendula umuntu owakhona wathi: Kanti ngubani uyise wabo\x + Isa. 54.13.\x*? Ngakho kwasekusiba yisaga \add ukuthi\add*: Kanti uSawuli laye uphakathi kwabaprofethi\x + 19.24. Mat. 13.54,55.\x*?
\v 13 Eseqedile ukuprofetha wafika endaweni ephakemeyo.
\p
\v 14 Uyise omncinyane kaSawuli wathi kuye lencekwini yakhe: Beliye ngaphi? Wasesithi: Ukuyadinga obabhemikazi; lapho sesibona ukuthi kabakho sasesifika kuSamuweli\x + 14.50.\x*.
\v 15 Uyise omncinyane kaSawuli wathi: Ake ungitshele ukuthi utheni kini uSamuweli?
\v 16 USawuli wasesithi kuyise omncinyane: Usitshelile sibili ukuthi obabhemikazi sebetholakele. Kodwa udaba lombuso akhuluma ngalo uSamuweli kamtshelanga\x + 9.20.\x*.
\p
\v 17 USamuweli wasebizela abantu ndawonye eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 11.15.\x* eMizipa\x + 7.5,6. Josh. 18.26.\x*;
\v 18 wathi kubantwana bakoIsrayeli: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Mina ngamenyusa uIsrayeli eGibhithe, ngalikhulula esandleni samaGibhithe lesandleni sayo yonke imibuso eyalicindezelayo\x + 12.8. Hlu. 6.8,9.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa lamuhla lina limalile uNkulunkulu wenu, yena ngokwakhe owalisindisayo engozini zonke zenu lensizini zenu; laselisithi kuye: Hatshi, beka inkosi phezu kwethu\x + 8.7,19. 12.12.\x*. Ngakho-ke manini phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngezizwe zenu langezinkulungwane zenu\x + Josh. 24.1.\x*.
\v 20 USamuweli wasesondeza zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli; njalo isizwe sakoBhenjamini sabanjwa\x + Josh. 7.14,16,17. Hlu. 20.9.\x*.
\v 21 Wasesondeza isizwe sakoBhenjamini ngensendo zaso, losendo lwakoMatiri lwabanjwa, loSawuli indodana kaKishi wabanjwa. Kuthe bemdinga katholakalanga.
\v 22 Ngakho babuya babuza eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ukuthi lowomuntu usezafika lapha yini? IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Khangelani, ucatshile empahleni\x + 23.2,4,9-11.\x*.
\v 23 Basebegijima bamlanda khona; lapho esemi phakathi kwabantu, wayemude kulabo bonke abantu kusukela ehlombe lakhe kusiya phezulu\x + 9.2.\x*.
\v 24 USamuweli wasesithi kubo bonke abantu: Liyambona yini lowo iN\nd kosi\nd* emkhethileyo, ukuthi kakho loyedwa onjengaye kubo bonke abantu? Bonke abantu basebememeza bathi: Kayiphile inkosi\x + 2 Sam. 21.6.\x*!
\v 25 USamuweli wasebatshela abantu indlela yombuso, wawubhala egwalweni, walubeka phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*. USamuweli wasebayekela bonke abantu bahamba, wonke waya endlini yakhe\x + 8.11. Dute. 17.14-20.\x*.
\p
\v 26 USawuli laye wasesiya endlini yakhe eGibeya\x + 11.4. Josh. 18.28.\x*; kwasekuhamba laye amaqhawe onhliziyo zawo uNkulunkulu wayezithintile.
\v 27 Kodwa\x + 11.12.\x* abantwana bakaBheliyali bathi: Uzasisindisa njani lo\x + Dute. 13.13.\x*? Basebemdelela, kabamphathelanga sipho; kodwa wazithulela\x + 16.20. 17.18. 25.27. Gen. 43.11. Hlu. 3.15. 2 Sam. 8.2,6. 1 Kho. 4.21. 10.25. 2 Lan. 17.5. Hlab. 72.10. Mat. 2.11. Zaga 18.16.\x*.